# CrossOver Project Structure

## Overview
CrossOver is an Electron-based crosshair overlay application with comprehensive cross-platform distribution support.

## Key Entry Points
- **Main Entry**: [index.js](mdc:index.js) - Application entry point
- **Main Process**: [src/main/crossover.js](mdc:src/main/crossover.js) - Core application logic
- **Window Management**: [src/main/windows.js](mdc:src/main/windows.js) - Window creation and management
- **Initialization**: [src/main/init.js](mdc:src/main/init.js) - App startup and IPC setup
- **Renderer**: [src/renderer/renderer.js](mdc:src/renderer/renderer.js) - Frontend logic

## Configuration Files
- **Package Config**: [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Dependencies, scripts, and electron-builder config
- **Playwright Testing**: [playwright.config.ts](mdc:playwright.config.ts) - Test configuration
- **Windows Build**: [electron-builder-windows.yaml](mdc:electron-builder-windows.yaml) - Windows-specific build settings
- **AppX Build**: [electron-builder-appx.yaml](mdc:electron-builder-appx.yaml) - Windows Store configuration

## Assets Structure
- **Icons**: [src/static/icons/](mdc:src/static/icons) - Platform-specific icons (PNG, ICO, ICNS)
- **Crosshairs**: [src/static/crosshairs/](mdc:src/static/crosshairs) - 25+ crosshair categories
- **Sounds**: [src/static/sounds/](mdc:src/static/sounds) - UI sound effects
- **Styles**: [src/renderer/styles/](mdc:src/renderer/styles) - SCSS stylesheets

## Production Files
- **Validation Script**: [scripts/validate-production.js](mdc:scripts/validate-production.js) - Production readiness checks
- **Release Checklist**: [RELEASE_CHECKLIST.md](mdc:RELEASE_CHECKLIST.md) - Pre-release validation steps
- **Production Plan**: [production-readiness-plan.md](mdc:production-readiness-plan.md) - Implementation roadmap
- **CI/CD**: [.github/workflows/production-validation.yml](mdc:.github/workflows/production-validation.yml) - Automated validation

## Testing Structure
- **Test Directory**: [test/](mdc:test) - Playwright test suites
- **Test Helpers**: [test/helpers.js](mdc:test/helpers.js) - Common test utilities
- **Test Results**: [test/results/](mdc:test/results) - Test output and artifacts

## Development Guidelines
- Keep files under 700 lines
- Use explicit variable names
- Follow existing code style
- Run production validation before releases
- Address security vulnerabilities promptly
